Package service.tut.pori.contentanalysis.video

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Definitions
    Definitions for video content analysis.
    DeletedVideoList
    A special video list used to list deleted video.
    Timecode
    A media object time code.
    TimecodeList
    A list of media object time codes.
    Video
    Contains metadata information of a single video.
    VideoAnalysisService
    This service enables content analysis and provides search features.
    VideoAnalysisTask
    Analysis task for video content.
    VideoBackendFeedbackTask
    An implementation of ASyncTask, meant for executing a back-end feedback task.
    VideoBackendFeedbackTask.FeedbackTaskBuilder
    A helper class building VideoTaskDetails usable with VideoBackendFeedbackTask and executable using VideoContentCore.scheduleTask(VideoTaskDetails)
    VideoContentCore
    Video content analysis core methods.
    VideoDAO
    The DAO for storing and retrieving video objects.
    VideoFeedbackTask
    An implementation of ASyncTask, meant for executing a feedback task.
    VideoFeedbackTask.FeedbackTaskBuilder
    A helper class building VideoTaskDetails usable with VideoFeedbackTask and executable using VideoContentCore.scheduleTask(VideoTaskDetails)
    VideoList
    This is a container class for video elements, which can be used directly with Response to provide XML output.
    VideoParameters
    Options for video analysis.
    VideoSearchCore
    Video search core methods.
    VideoSearchTask
    Search task used to query back-ends for results.
    VideoTaskDAO
    Class for storing video tasks
    VideoTaskDetails
    An implementation of AbstractTaskDetails, which can be used to define a video analysis task, or a feedback task.
    VideoTaskResponse
    Class for representing a response received from a back-end to a previously submitted analysis task.
